hwt.bodyText:
If((clk)._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0x0),
        wr_ptr(0x0),
        rd_ptr(0x0),
        looped(0x0),
    ).Else(
        wr_ptr(wr_ptr_next),
        rd_ptr(rd_ptr_next),
        looped(looped_next),
    ),
)

If((clk)._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0x0),
        wWordCntr(0x0),
        wErrFlag(0x0),
        lastReqDispatched(0x1),
    ).Else(
        wWordCntr(wWordCntr_next),
        wErrFlag(wErrFlag_next),
        lastReqDispatched(lastReqDispatched_next),
    ),
)

If(lastReqDispatched,
    id(driver_req_id),
    a_addr(driver_req_addr),
    If(driver_req_len > 0xff,
        a_len(0xff),
    ).Else(
        a_len(sig_),
    ),
    req_idBackup_next(driver_req_id),
    addrBackup_next(((driver_req_addr)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32, signed=False, forceVector=True)) + 2048)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32, forceVector=True))),
    lenDebth_next(((driver_req_len)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(9, signed=False, forceVector=True)) - 256)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(9, forceVector=True))),
    If(sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd & a_ready & driver_req_vld,
        If(driver_req_len > 0xff,
            lastReqDispatched_next(0x0),
        ).Else(
            lastReqDispatched_next(0x1),
        ),
    ).Else(
        lastReqDispatched_next(lastReqDispatched),
    ),
    driver_req_rd(a_ready & sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd),
    a_valid(driver_req_vld & sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd & (~wErrFlag)),
    sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_vld(driver_req_vld & a_ready),
).Else(
    id(req_idBackup),
    a_addr(addrBackup),
    If(lenDebth > 0xff,
        a_len(0xff),
    ).Else(
        a_len(sig_),
    ),
    a_valid(sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd & (~wErrFlag)),
    sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_vld(a_ready),
    driver_req_rd(0x0),
    If(sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd & a_ready,
        addrBackup_next(((addrBackup)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32, signed=False, forceVector=True)) + 2048)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32, forceVector=True))),
        lenDebth_next(((lenDebth)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(9, signed=False, forceVector=True)) - 256)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(9, forceVector=True))),
        If(lenDebth <= 0xff,
            lastReqDispatched_next(0x1),
        ).Else(
            lastReqDispatched_next(lastReqDispatched),
        ),
    ).Else(
        addrBackup_next(addrBackup),
        lenDebth_next(lenDebth),
        lastReqDispatched_next(lastReqDispatched),
    ),
    req_idBackup_next(req_idBackup),
)

If((clk)._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0x0),
        wr_ptr(0x0),
        rd_ptr(0x0),
        looped(0x0),
    ).Else(
        wr_ptr(wr_ptr_next),
        rd_ptr(rd_ptr_next),
        looped(looped_next),
    ),
)
